data.description:
Contract fell through at no fault of the seller.
Welcome to your coastal paradise in Long Beach, Mississippi! This magnificent 2 bedroom, 2 bath townhouse offers the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and breathtaking beach views. With its prime location, two balconies, open living spaces, three levels, garage, elevator, and close proximity to the pool and beaches, this home is the epitome of coastal living at its finest.
As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a spacious and inviting open floor plan, designed to maximize natural light and capture the essence of beachside living. The living area is the ideal space to relax and entertain, with plenty of room for gathering with loved ones or enjoying a quiet evening at home. Large windows allow for an abundance of sunlight, while offering stunning views of the nearby beach.
The kitchen features modern appliances, ample counter space, and stylish cabinetry. Whether you're preparing a quick snack or hosting a dinner party, this well-appointed kitchen has everything you need to whip up some culinary delights.
Make your way upstairs and discover the two generously sized bedrooms, with the master having a private balcony with beach views. Wake up to the soothing sounds of the ocean, sip your morning coffee, and watch the waves roll in from the comfort of your own private retreat. The bedrooms are designed with your comfort in mind, providing ample space and storage for all your needs.
With three levels, this townhouse offers plenty of room for privacy and flexibility. The ground level features a convenient garage, providing secure parking for your vehicle and additional storage space for beach gear and outdoor equipment. The presence of an elevator adds to the convenience, ensuring easy access to all levels of the home.
Just a short stroll away, you'll find a sparkling community pool where you can cool off on warm summer days or simply unwind with a book in hand. When you're ready to feel the sand between your toes, the beautiful beaches are just a short walk from your doorstep, offering endless opportunities for relaxation and recreation.
Located in the charming community of Long Beach, this townhouse provides easy access to local shops, dining establishments, and a vibrant coastal lifestyle. Embrace the tranquility of beach living while still being within reach of modern conveniences and entertainment options.
Don't miss the chance to own this incredible beachside townhouse in Long Beach, Mississippi. Seize the opportunity to experience the coastal lifestyle you've always dreamed of, with beach views, open living spaces, multiple balconies, and a host of desirable amenities. Schedule your private showing today and start living your coastal dream!
